HEADWORD: Cockspur
<hw>Cock"spur</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
variety of <gen>Crat⟦ae⟧gus</gen>, or hawthorn (<spn>Crat⟦ae⟧gus
